                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I set different clusters for &quot;spark.hadoop.fs.defaultFS&quot; and &quot;spark.yarn.stagingDir&quot; as follows&#65306;&lt;/p&gt;

